originalText.text:
I came across their stall at the Christmas Market located at Bryant Park.

I was totally impressed by their products, display and sales personnel  who were very helpful, polite and non-pushy. For myself, that is a pleasant and great shopping experience.

The manager at the cashiers was equally professional and polite. I was doubly impressed by their packaging of a sturdy elegant white gift bag with black ribbons, very classy!
I will be a regular customer for sure.

authorAttribution.displayName: By the Rising Of the Moon

originalText.text: Candles, diffusers, and body care products in the best scents(strong but not overpowering and has a clean scent lacking the chemical tone you get with yankee candles). You know when you are about 50 feet from the store on a calm day because you can smell the scents coming into the open door. Extremely friendly staff and great products. Probably one of the best places to go if you need some gifts quickly. They have the larger candles and diffusers beautifully packaged for gift presentation.

originalText.text: This place is an absolute gem of a place.  Amazing scents in gorgeous packaging for very fair prices.  The associate was incredibly helpful and friendly.  I ordered a few things online, and the arrived the next day and included a special sample.  Really impressed with this small business.
